  </dd>
  
  <hr /><a name="languageflags"></a>
  <dt style="font-weight: bold">LANGUAGE FLAGS</dt>
  <dd>See &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvl2.html#linguisticflags">linguistic flags</a>&rsquo;.
  <p>
  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d1328.gif">
